title: Bohm (Dr. Joannes)
body: E.: Some Fossils from the Salvages Islands. (Reprint from the Journal of the German Geological Society, year 1898). This work records 7 species, including 2 new ones: Nerita salvagensis and Cabralia Schmitzii.

Dr. Joannes Bohm: Author of the work 'Some Fossils from the Salvages Islands'

1898: Year of publication of the work 'Some Fossils from the Salvages Islands'
